cy-since-1815-a-study-in-small full text at Questia]\n* Vandenbosch, Amry. ''The neutrality of the Netherlands during the world war'' (1927).\n* Wielenga, Friso. ''A History of the Netherlands: From the Sixteenth Century to the Present Day'' (2015) 344 pp\n\n{{refend}}\n\n===Geography and environment===\n{{refbegin}}\n* Burke, Gerald L. ''The making of Dutch towns: A study in urban development from the 10th\u201317th centuries'' (1960)\n*  Lambert, Audrey M. ''The Making of the Dutch Landscape: An Historical Geography of the Netherlands'' (1985); focus on the history of land reclamation\n* Meijer, Henk. ''Compact geography of The Netherlands''  (1985)\n* Riley, R. C., and G. J. Ashworth. ''Benelux: An Economic Geography of Belgium, the Netherlands, and Luxembourg'' (1975) [https://www.questia.com/read/85882918/benelux-an-economic-geography-of-belgium-the-netherlands online]\n{{refend}}\n\n== External links ==\n{{Commons category|History of the Netherlands}}\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20041013072113/http://www.20eeuwennederland.nl/periodes Chronologisch overzicht van de Nederlandse geschiedenis (in Dutch)]\n* [http://dutchrevolt.leidenuniv.nl/Nederlands/default.htm De Tachtigjarige Oorlog (in Dutch)]\n* [http://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/maney/dtc/ ''Dutch Crossing: Journal of Low Countries Studies''], a scholarly journal\n* [http://www.gutenberg.org/etext/14971 History of Holland, George Edmundson, 1922, Project Gutenberg EBook.]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20120926161214/http://www.innl.nl/page/14332/en History of the Netherlands from 50 BC to 2005]\n* [http://eudocs.lib.byu.edu/index.php/History_of_the_Netherlands:_Primary_Documents History of Netherlands: Primary Documents]\n* [http://www.niod.nl/ Netherlands Institute for War Documentation]\n* [http://www.infoplease.com/country/netherlands.html Netherlands: Maps, History, Geography, Government, Culture, Facts, Guide & Travel &#124; Infoplease.com]\n* [http://www.historical-novel.com/ Overview of his